name: Tube O Life (Listen)
description: Tube O Life: This is the 10th of my #eVeRyDay Animation and Music Production. Unfortunatly this render would have taken a week, so there is an extra long song as a bunus. Eventually I see in the future, Tube O Life having an animated sibling. Time will tell. Tools used: Cinema 4D, Redshift, Universal Audio Apollo & UA Plugins, Fender Amp, Fender P Bass, Roland TD-17 E-Drums, Superior Drummer 3,Ableton Live, PRS, ESP, Moog Subsequent 37, Moog Matriarch
